ZH: 留神走路，不要摔倒。
EN: Be careful while walking, don't fall down.

ZH: 上下班的时候要留神交通状况。
EN: Pay attention to the traffic conditions when commuting.

ZH: 在陌生地方旅行时要留神财物安全。
EN: Be cautious about the safety of your belongings when traveling in unfamiliar places.

ZH: 留神狗的反应，不要惹它们生气。
EN: Pay attention to the dogs' reactions, don't make them angry.

ZH: 汽车行驶的时候要留神路况。
EN: Pay attention to the road conditions when driving a car.

ZH: 外出时要留神天气预报，带上雨伞或披风。
EN: Pay attention to the weather forecast when going out, bring an umbrella or a raincoat.

ZH: 留神大家耳朵里的隐形耳机，不要遗失。
EN: Pay attention to the invisible earphones in everyone's ears, don't lose them.

ZH: 路边的行人要留神行驶的车辆。
EN: Pedestrians on the roadside need to watch out for passing vehicles.

ZH: 留神电池电量，给手机充电。
EN: Pay attention to the battery level and charge your phone.

ZH: 登山的时候要留神脚下，防止滑倒。
EN: Pay attention to your steps while climbing, to avoid slipping.

ZH: 留神文章里的错别字，避免出现错误。
EN: Pay attention to the typos in the article, to avoid mistakes.

ZH: 购物时要留神货物的保质期。
EN: Pay attention to the expiration dates of the goods when shopping.

ZH: 留神病人的病情变化，及时就医。
EN: Pay attention to the changes in the patient's condition and seek medical help promptly.

