EN: Pay attention to choosing environmentally friendly materials when renovating a house.

ZH: 喂养宠物时要留神食物的摄入量。
EN: Pay attention to the amount of food intake when feeding pets.

ZH: 留神护肤品的成分，避免过敏反应。
EN: Pay attention to the ingredients of skincare products, to avoid allergic reactions.

ZH: 留神银行账户的安全，不要随意透露密码。
EN: Pay attention to the security of your bank account and do not disclose your password casually.

ZH: 饮食要留神营养均衡，保持健康。
EN: Pay attention to a balanced diet and maintain good health.

